quran[75]{c,v,t}:
  87,1,Senin innde joom Ma ɓurnde toowde
  87,2,Oon takɗo O fonndi
  87,3,Oon koddirɗo refti O feewni
  87,4,Oon yaltinɗo durngol
  87,5,O watti ngol yoorko wayliiko
  87,6,Ma Min njanngin Ma A yeɓjjittah
  87,7,Si wonah ko Alla haaji pellet hombo anndi ko feeñi e ko wirnii
  87,8,Min newnan Ma na newori
  87,9,Siftinir ɗoon ɗo ciftanirgol na nafata
  87,10,Ma waacta oon kulɗo Alla
  87,11,Woɗɗitoo mbo ɓurɗo hiiteede
  87,12,Oon naatoowo yiite mannge nge
  87,13,Refti o maayatah toon o wuuratah
  87,14,Malaama oon laaɓɗo e sirku
  87,15,O jantii Innde joom makko o juuli
  87,16,"Ko woni, ko hoɗon ɓurna nguurndam aduna"
  87,17,Ko laakira ɓuri moƴƴude e heddaade
  87,18,ɗum ina e ɗereeji gadiiɗi
  87,19,ɗereeji Ibraahiima e Muusa
  88,1,taw si arii e maaɗa Yewtere fii darngal
  88,2,Geece ñande heen na koyi
  88,3,Gollooje tampuɗe
  88,4,Hoɗe naata yiite wulnge
  88,5,Hombo yarnee e seewnde wulnde sanne
  88,6,ɓe ngalah ñaamdu si wonah puɗi Darii
  88,7,ɗi paynatah ɗi nafath e heege
  88,8,Geece malaabe ñande heen na pooyni
  88,9,Hoɗe mbelaa golle mum en
  88,10,E nder Aljanna toowuɗo
  88,11,A nanatah heen bolle meere
  88,12,Ina e hembo seewnde iloore
  88,13,Ina e hembo leece ɓamtaaɗe
  88,14,E kaasuuji keblaaɗi ngam yarde
  88,15,E ngaflaaje potndaaɗe
  88,16,E mbettudi na sara kala bannge
  88,17,Mbela ɓe ndaaraani na ngelooba tagira
  88,18,E kammu hono mbo ɓamtira
  88,19,E pelle hono ɗe ndarnira
  88,20,E leydi ndi hono ndi wertira
  88,21,Waajo Aan ka A baajatooɗo
  88,22,A wonah baawnoowo ɓe
  88,23,Si wonah oon dunttiɗo o yeddi
  88,24,Alla lepta mbo lepte ɓurɗe mawnude
  88,25,Pellet ko Amen woni ruttorde maɓɓe
  88,26,Refti ko e Amen woni haasboore maɓɓe
  89,1,Alla woondirii Fajiri
  89,2,E balɗe sappa
  89,3,Mi woondiri kala ko ɗimmita e ko teelɗi
  89,4,Mi woondarii jemma si mbo arii e niɓɓidde
  89,5,Mbela ina e ndee woondoore jaɓnoore jom hakkille
  89,6,Mbela a yi*aani na joom ma waɗi Aad en
  89,7,Iram jom doosɗe
  89,8,Mbo hono mum tagaaka e leydi
  89,9,E Samuud ɓeen seekɓe kaaƴe to caatngol
  89,10,E Fir*awna jom penɗe
  89,11,ɓeen bewnooɓe to leydi
  89,12,ɓe kebbini e hendi bonannde
  89,13,joom Ma yuppi e maɓɓe lepte cattuɗe
  89,14,joom Ma na tommbiiɓe
  89,15,Tawi ko neɓɗɗanke si joom Makko jarabiimo mbo O teddani mbo O neemini mbo o wiyat joom am teddinii kam
  89,16,Si tawii noon O jaribiimo mbo O faaɗni arsuko makko o wiya joom am hoynii kam
  89,17,"Alah wonah noon, ko woni ko on teddintaana baaya"
  89,18,o rerɗiŋtaa e ñammiingol miskiino
  89,19,Hoɗon ñaama ndonu ñaamgol cattungol
  89,20,Hoɗon njiɗi jawdi jiɗgol cattungol
  89,21,"Alah ɗum haanaani, si leydi ndii dimmbaama dimmbugol"
  89,22,joom ma ardi e malaykaaji hoɗi mbaɗi saffeeji. @Corrected
  89,23,jahanama addee ñande heen neɗɗo siftoro kono hol ko siftorde nafata
  89,24,O wi*a haaniino mi ardinii golle lobbe wonande nguurndam am
  89,25,E oon ñalawma hay gooto leptatah hono lepte makko
  89,26,Hay gooto tonngetaake hono tonngi heeferɓe
  89,27,Eehey ma fittaandu huɓandiindu
  89,28,Rutto e joom ma haɗa woni belaaɗo Mbo Kanko ne hombo wela ma
  89,29,Naat e maccuɓe Am
  89,30,Naat e aljanna Am